Introduction

Seung Yeop is a South Korean singer under E Entertainment. He is a member of the boy group E'LAST.

On August 21, 2019, he was announced as a member of the upcoming boy group, then known as EBOYZ. Now called E'LAST, the group made their official debut on June 9, 2020 with the mini album Day Dream.
